üá¨üáß Whitepaper: GoodLuckcoin (GLC)

1. Introduction

GoodLuckcoin (GLC) is a revolutionary cryptocurrency built on the TON blockchain, powered by a unique consensus mechanism called Proof of Fortune (PoF). GLC introduces randomness, gamification, and accessibility into the blockchain space, making participation fun, fair, and open to everyone.

---

2. Vision

GLC aims to redefine how people interact with digital assets by turning blockchain into a game of chance, strategy, and community. We believe that luck, when combined with transparency and technology, can create a more inclusive crypto economy.

---

3. Key Features

| Feature              | Description                                                  |
|----------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| Blockchain           | TON (The Open Network)                                       |
| Token Type           | Jetton                                                       |
| Ticker               | GLC                                                          |
| Total Supply         | 1,000,000,000,000 GLC                                        |
| Consensus Mechanism  | Proof of Fortune (PoF)                                       |
| Telegram Integration | Full support via @GoodLuckBot                               |
| NFT Talismans        | Collectible items that boost luck and unlock bonuses         |

---

4. Proof of Fortune (PoF)

PoF is a novel consensus model where validators are selected randomly using cryptographic functions (VRF), rather than by stake or computing power. Every eligible node has a chance to be chosen, making the system democratic and unpredictable.

- VRF-based randomness ensures fairness and transparency  
- Luck Level and NFT Talismans can boost selection chances  
- Daily PoF Draws reward active participants with GLC and NFTs  
- Gamified mechanics encourage engagement and retention

---

5. Telegram Ecosystem

GLC lives inside Telegram through the interactive bot @GoodLuckBot, which offers:

- üé∞ Daily Fortune Spins  
- üßø NFT Gallery and upgrades  
- üìà Luck Level tracking  
- üëõ Wallet management  
- üéÆ Mini-games and quests

---

6. Tokenomics

| Allocation           | Percentage |
|----------------------|------------|
| Community & Airdrops | 40%        |
| Development          | 20%        |
| Reserve              | 15%        |
| Partnerships         | 10%        |
| Team                 | 10%        |
| Charity Fund         | 5%         |

---

7. Roadmap

Q4 2028
- Token launch on TON  
- Telegram bot release  
- First NFT drop

Q1 2029
- Mini-games integration  
- PoF staking mechanics  
- Community voting

Q2 2030
- Charity fund activation  
- Mobile wallet release  
- Strategic partnerships

---

8. Conclusion

GLC is more than a token ‚Äî it‚Äôs a movement. By combining luck, blockchain, and community, GoodLuckcoin creates a playful and inclusive ecosystem where anyone can win, and everyone belongs.

